| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2994 — Recovery Inhibition (direwolf)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2ac0d751-ed9e-5699-9c98-0ba65bb3a13d"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
